credit-megan-cullen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nick-cave-credit-megan-cullen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/nick-cave-credit-megan-cullen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds">Nick Cave 和 The Bad Seeds</a>分享了他们即将发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds-announce-new-wild-god-album-preorder-3597587">Wild God</a> 》中的第三首单曲《Long Dark Night》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/nick-cave-interview-hope-faith-carnage-new-bad-seeds-grinderman-cancel-culture-coronation-3448005"><b>尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）：“没有任何衡量标准表明美德造就优秀的艺术”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌的灵感来自西班牙16世纪诗人圣十字约翰的诗《<em>灵魂的暗夜》</em> ，呼应了危机、斗争和超越的主题。</p><p>在这首内省的民谣中，凯夫唱道：“<em>讲述一个梦，当你所做的一切都在做梦时/但事情并不那么美好，我无法轻视它/我可怜的灵魂，那是一个漆黑的夜晚/这是一个漫长的夜晚，一个星期，也许是一年。”</em></p><p>凯夫解释说，这首歌的灵感来自于“有史以来最伟大、最有力的皈依诗”之一，并补充道：“不过，归根结底，这是一首美丽的乡村曲调。感觉就像《Wild God》这首歌的甜蜜伴侣。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nick Cave &amp; The Bad Seeds - Long Dark Night（歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/J7cgUhkEB_U?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>即将发行的专辑的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds-announce-new-wild-god-album-preorder-3597587">同名歌曲</a>于三月份作为主打单曲发行，紧随其后的是五月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-share-exuberant-new-single-frogs-it-just-puts-a-big-fucking-smile-on-my-face-3760636">“充满活力”的“Frogs”</a> 。您可以<a href="https://nickcave-badseeds.ffm.to/wild-god" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订黑胶唱片</a>。</p><p> 《Wild God》将于 8 月 30 日发行，Cave 表示希望这张 10 首曲目的唱片能够对听众产生和他自己一样的效果。 “它从扬声器中爆发出来，我被它所吸引，”他说。 “这是一张复杂的唱片，但它也具有深刻而令人愉悦的感染力。</p><p> “当我们录制唱片时，从来没有一个总体规划。这些唱片反映了演奏它们的作家和音乐家的情感状态。听着这个，我不知道，看来我们很高兴，”他补充道。 “这张唱片没有任何废话。当它击中时，它就击中了。它会提升你。它让你感动。我喜欢这一点。” </p><figure id="attachment_3597754" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3597754" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3597754" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="《狂野之神》专辑封面" width="2000" height="2007" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-800x803.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-1392x1397.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Wild-God-Artwork@2000x2000-1068x1072.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3597754" class="wp-caption-text"> 《狂野之神》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>为了庆祝《Wild God》的发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-announces-wild-god-qa-session-in-london-3772930">Cave 宣布将于 8 月 29 日星期四在伦敦举办由 Rough Trade 主办的独家问答环节。</a>观众将有机会在正式发行前首次完整聆听这张专辑，并直接向主唱提出问题。</p><p>粉丝们可以在 8 月 15 日星期四下午 5 点（英国夏令时）之前<a href="https://www.roughtrade.com/en-gb/product/nick-cave-and-the-bad-seeds/wild-god-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">通过 Rough Trade 预订《Wild God》，</a>参加抽奖，获得参加比赛的机会。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-says-writing-songs-is-a-fucking-nightmare-3774395"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在其他地方，Cave 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-add-extra-dates-to-2024-uk-and-european-wild-god-tour-buy-tickets-3618043">宣布了 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演</a>将于今年 9 月在德国拉开帷幕，持续到 10 月，然后在 11 月进行英国巡演。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-tickets/artist/743143?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=W1fRUUS0ZxyPUR9RiQWj01vfUkHWQc1hhRjN2c0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>（英国和爱尔兰）和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fnick-cave-the-bad-seeds-tickets%2Fartist%2F743143" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（欧洲）购买门票。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-the-bad-seeds-share-beautiful-country-tune-long-dark-night-3777117">Nick Cave 和 The Bad Seeds 分享的“美丽乡村曲调”“Long Dark Night”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
